1
00:01:30,900 --> 00:01:34,990
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,150 --> 00:01:35,920
Open your eyes wide

3
00:01:35,789 --> 00:01:39,440
[2024]

4
00:01:35,920 --> 00:01:37,180
and look for yourself—

5
00:01:37,229 --> 00:01:38,690
where do you think you are?

6
00:01:38,870 --> 00:01:40,000
This is Shengcheng!

7
00:01:40,509 --> 00:01:41,710
Top university grads,

8
00:01:41,710 --> 00:01:43,039
those who studied abroad—

9
00:01:43,039 --> 00:01:44,509
every single one of them
swallows their pride

10
00:01:44,509 --> 00:01:45,910
and works like a dog here!

11
00:01:46,430 --> 00:01:47,229
I'm telling you,

12
00:01:47,229 --> 00:01:48,640
if you still want to keep your job,

13
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,840
swallow

14
00:01:50,039 --> 00:01:50,950
whatever you shouldn't have said

15
00:01:50,950 --> 00:01:52,150
and keep your mouth shut!

16
00:01:52,150 --> 00:01:52,789
Mr. Wang,

17
00:01:53,150 --> 00:01:54,120
there's a detail in the contract

18
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,979
I'd like to go over with you again!

19
00:02:01,510 --> 00:02:02,760
Thank you, Ms. Xia.

20
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:05,340
It's okay. Don't be too upset.

21
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,430
Since when did you start liking

22
00:02:15,430 --> 00:02:17,280
meddling in other people's business?

23
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:19,210
Just what's left of my conscience.

24
00:02:20,190 --> 00:02:23,250
Be careful, or your conscience
will get you in trouble.

25
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:29,900
[Episode 35: Do You Dare Face Yourself?]

26
00:02:31,579 --> 00:02:35,690
[Kong Island]

27
00:02:32,110 --> 00:02:33,640
Still nothing newsworthy.

28
00:02:34,030 --> 00:02:36,030
Yeah, total waste of film.

29
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,800
Do you think Mr. Du will ever wake up?

30
00:02:39,470 --> 00:02:41,030
He's been in a coma for so long.

31
00:02:41,030 --> 00:02:42,690
If he wakes up, I'll eat my hat.

32
00:02:42,770 --> 00:02:45,079
You think we've been waiting here
all this time

33
00:02:45,079 --> 00:02:46,340
just for him to wake up?

34
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:48,079
After waiting this long,

35
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:50,240
of course, we're here
to grab the first scoop.

36
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:52,840
Exactly, now that's something
worth hearing.

37
00:02:57,590 --> 00:02:58,079
Dad.

38
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:00,800
Dad!

39
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:04,220
Haven't visited in a few days.

40
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,710
Did you miss me?

41
00:03:07,590 --> 00:03:08,960
Probably not.

42
00:03:09,470 --> 00:03:10,590
Anyway, every day,

43
00:03:10,910 --> 00:03:13,040
you have Vivi putting on a show for you.

44
00:03:18,030 --> 00:03:19,230
And speaking of that,

45
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,260
you should be thanking me.

46
00:03:21,590 --> 00:03:23,079
I paid for Vivi's

47
00:03:23,310 --> 00:03:25,240
face and body—the whole makeover.

48
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:27,630
You should've seen

49
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:29,230
what she looked like before.

50
00:03:30,079 --> 00:03:30,840
So tacky.

51
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,550
Just stay in your coma!

52
00:03:39,710 --> 00:03:41,400
I've sold the whole shipping business!

53
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,470
I'll sell the entire

54
00:03:42,470 --> 00:03:43,240
Chengrong Group too!

55
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,190
Do you believe me?

56
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:45,030
Do you?

57
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,590
You're really not going to wake up?

58
00:03:56,590 --> 00:03:57,590
That won't do.

59
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,190
Then how will you see

60
00:03:59,190 --> 00:04:00,590
how capable I've become?

61
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,470
How will you feel

62
00:04:02,470 --> 00:04:04,470
what it's like to be abandoned
by everyone?

63
00:04:04,470 --> 00:04:05,670
If you stay like this,

64
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:07,680
how am I supposed to get my revenge?

65
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,920
Take good care of him.

66
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,800
Anything unusual lately?

67
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,310
Ms. Vivi

68
00:04:32,310 --> 00:04:34,040
comes to visit Mr. Du every day.

69
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:36,210
Let her come if she wants to.

70
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,000
If she actually

71
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,130
wakes the old man up,

72
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,980
I'll have to give her a big reward.

73
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:44,740
Ms. Vivi,

74
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,270
you're truly devoted

75
00:04:45,270 --> 00:04:46,390
to the old man.

76
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,760
If he really wakes up,

77
00:04:48,930 --> 00:04:50,860
he'll definitely reward you well.

78
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,680
I'm going in to check on the Master.

79
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,010
I should be thanking you

80
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:56,930
for giving me the chance
to play the dutiful son.

81
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,430
I'm going in to check on the Master.

82
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:01,690
No one is stopping you.

83
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:08,110
Shit! Shit!

84
00:05:08,110 --> 00:05:09,240
Shit! Young Master!

85
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:11,760
Mrs. Du is on the roof,
threatening to jump!

86
00:05:11,860 --> 00:05:12,830
Why are you just standing there?

87
00:05:12,830 --> 00:05:13,960
Come with me, quick!

88
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:14,430
Yes.

89
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:15,870
Calm down! Calm down!

90
00:05:15,870 --> 00:05:17,120
Don't come any closer!

91
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:17,800
Step back!

92
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:19,310
Step back!

93
00:05:19,390 --> 00:05:20,310
-Calm down!
-Calm down!

94
00:05:20,310 --> 00:05:20,920
You too!

95
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:23,390
Back off! Step back!

96
00:05:23,510 --> 00:05:24,510
I'm going to jump!

97
00:05:29,070 --> 00:05:30,600
Out of the way! Out of the way!

98
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:33,870
Stop filming!
Go point that camera at your own wife!

99
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,070
Du Zhaohui,

100
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:37,560
you have the nerve to show your face?

101
00:05:38,310 --> 00:05:39,640
You harmed your own dad,

102
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:40,920
framed Zhaoji,

103
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:42,920
and colluded with Mr. Cheng

104
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,159
to forge the power of attorney

105
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:45,420
to take over the group!

106
00:05:45,510 --> 00:05:46,950
You wolf in sheep's clothing—

107
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:49,550
you didn't even spare
your own flesh and blood!

108
00:05:49,630 --> 00:05:50,490
Mr. Du Zhaohui,

109
00:05:50,630 --> 00:05:51,680
is what Mrs. Du said true?

110
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:52,630
Of course, it's true!

111
00:05:52,630 --> 00:05:54,190
Every word I say is true!

112
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,720
You reporters,

113
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:57,510
you just love the drama, don't you?

114
00:05:57,510 --> 00:05:58,670
Don't block the medical staff!

115
00:05:58,670 --> 00:05:59,720
Kick them all out!

116
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:00,840
Kick them out!

117
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,040
Don't go!

118
00:06:02,950 --> 00:06:04,120
He's lying!

119
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:05,160
I'm telling the truth!

120
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,070
Don't leave!

121
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,090
Auntie Song,

122
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,940
do you really want to jump?

123
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,600
From this height,

124
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,870
you probably won't die.

125
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:15,390
It'll just hurt a lot.

126
00:06:21,270 --> 00:06:22,430
Stop agitating her!

127
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:24,320
Don't come closer! Back off!

128
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,360
Back off!

129
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,830
They've forced me.

130
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:45,680
Don't blame me.

131
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,920
It'll be quick.

132
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:52,020
You won't suffer for long.

133
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,650
I'm actually...

134
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,430
setting you free.

135
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:02,380
If you had considered me a bit more,

136
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,360
I wouldn't have been in

137
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:06,420
such an embarrassing situation now.

138
00:07:07,870 --> 00:07:09,510
I tried so hard to please you,

139
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:13,640
just to make sure
you can't live without me.

140
00:07:14,070 --> 00:07:15,000
But did you really think

141
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:17,000
I like being with an old man like you?

142
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,690
If it weren't for survival,

143
00:07:20,270 --> 00:07:21,600
who would do any of this?

144
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:23,830
You said

145
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:25,270
you'd give me a life of luxury.

146
00:07:25,270 --> 00:07:26,560
But what happened?

147
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:29,310
You don't care about me at all.

148
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:38,000
Old fool.

149
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,960
You got to enjoy such a young

150
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,320
and beautiful body.

151
00:08:43,630 --> 00:08:44,690
You came out ahead.

152
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:52,000
What do you think you're doing?

153
00:08:57,870 --> 00:08:58,400
It's you!

154
00:08:58,630 --> 00:08:59,560
You want me dead!

155
00:08:59,870 --> 00:09:01,270
You want your own father dead

156
00:09:01,270 --> 00:09:02,320
and Zhaoji too!

157
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:03,370
Young Master Du!

158
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:05,000
Your father has woken up.

159
00:09:06,790 --> 00:09:07,790
Did you hear that?

160
00:09:07,910 --> 00:09:09,040
The old man is awake.

161
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,270
Go ahead and jump.

162
00:09:10,270 --> 00:09:12,130
He can even arrange your funeral.

163
00:09:12,790 --> 00:09:14,060
Mrs. Du, stop messing around!

164
00:09:14,060 --> 00:09:15,990
You'll have to pay if you damage it!

165
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,320
He's awake?

166
00:09:20,790 --> 00:09:21,920
How could he wake up?

167
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:23,970
How could he wake up?

168
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,570
What should I do now?

169
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,330
What should I do now?

170
00:09:31,870 --> 00:09:32,720
What do I do?

171
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,120
What do I do?

172
00:10:05,790 --> 00:10:06,910
Ms. Vivi,

173
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,210
impressive.

174
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:11,130
You even managed to wake the old man up.

175
00:10:12,150 --> 00:10:13,750
That's a great achievement.

176
00:10:15,030 --> 00:10:16,120
It's all because

177
00:10:16,870 --> 00:10:18,070
he's favored by fate.

178
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,030
Young Master Du.

179
00:10:23,030 --> 00:10:24,030
Doctor, how is he?

180
00:10:24,150 --> 00:10:25,360
Your father's intracranial hemorrhage

181
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,820
hasn't fully cleared yet.

182
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:27,750
We still need to wait for

183
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:30,070
the detailed examination report
for specifics.

184
00:10:30,070 --> 00:10:31,120
But the good news is,

185
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,910
he has regained consciousness.

186
00:10:32,910 --> 00:10:33,970
Thank you, doctor.

187
00:10:34,030 --> 00:10:35,630
Your father wants to see you.

188
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,550
He has something to tell you.

189
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:37,900
Okay.

190
00:10:37,940 --> 00:10:38,870
Thank you, doctor.

191
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:39,200
Okay.

192
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:41,030
Hua.

193
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:42,600
Lock down this entire floor.

194
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,960
Don't let any reporters in,

195
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,960
and don't let anyone out.

196
00:10:46,270 --> 00:10:46,910
Got it.

197
00:10:53,350 --> 00:10:54,060
Ms. Vivi.

198
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,010
What do you want?

199
00:10:56,630 --> 00:10:57,030
I...

200
00:10:58,510 --> 00:10:59,910
You must want some water.

201
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:01,920
Get some water for Ms. Vivi.

202
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:05,040
You've had a long day. Sit down and rest.

203
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:09,000
You also heard the young master—
no one's allowed to leave.

204
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:11,000
Don't make things difficult for me.

205
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:28,290
Hungry after waking up?

206
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,090
Wanna a banana, Dad?

207
00:11:32,550 --> 00:11:34,010
Don't look at me like that.

208
00:11:34,030 --> 00:11:34,890
Let me tell you,

209
00:11:35,500 --> 00:11:36,320
I've already sold

210
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,980
the entire shipping company.

211
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,480
There was no stopping it.

212
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:41,410
The contracts are already signed.

213
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:45,850
Our family has come to this.

214
00:11:46,270 --> 00:11:47,000
Besides,

215
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:49,490
why would I stop you?

216
00:11:53,150 --> 00:11:54,480
And as for the smuggling business,

217
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:56,010
I've completely removed it

218
00:11:56,150 --> 00:11:57,520
from our family's operations.

219
00:11:57,520 --> 00:11:58,500
Does that hurt?

220
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:00,870
But in the long run,

221
00:12:00,870 --> 00:12:01,960
it's good for

222
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:03,640
our Chengrong Group.

223
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:05,840
As for your Liu Keying,

224
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:06,570
she ran away.

225
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:07,600
Your wife

226
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:08,800
is up on the roof,

227
00:12:08,910 --> 00:12:10,510
making a scene
in front of every media outlet,

228
00:12:10,510 --> 00:12:11,710
threatening to jump.

229
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,460
Go up and talk her down?

230
00:12:15,390 --> 00:12:16,630
I'm not interested.

231
00:12:18,510 --> 00:12:19,360
Then what about your son?

232
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:21,210
Do you care about Du Zhaoji?

233
00:12:24,630 --> 00:12:25,630
He's downstairs.

234
00:12:31,270 --> 00:12:32,070
Young Master.

235
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,460
Du Chengrong has woken up.

236
00:12:40,150 --> 00:12:42,280
Since he's tough enough to survive...

237
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:44,890
Start the boat!

238
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:45,670
Yes!

239
00:12:58,030 --> 00:12:58,630
No way!

240
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,200
You put so much effort

241
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,750
into raising this son of yours.

242
00:13:01,750 --> 00:13:03,550
Don't you feel anything for him?

243
00:13:05,790 --> 00:13:08,630
That brat tried to kill his own dad.

244
00:13:09,430 --> 00:13:11,360
He must bear all the consequences.

245
00:13:15,510 --> 00:13:16,000
Yong!

246
00:13:23,150 --> 00:13:23,780
Yong!

247
00:13:26,030 --> 00:13:27,230
Get ready to head out!

248
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,520
Where is the captain?

249
00:13:29,370 --> 00:13:30,300
What's going on?

250
00:13:31,910 --> 00:13:32,670
Yong!

251
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:34,220
What happened?

252
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:35,860
Start the boat!

253
00:13:36,390 --> 00:13:37,050
Don't move,

254
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:37,540
police!

255
00:13:45,550 --> 00:13:45,880
Move!

256
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:47,970
Hurry up!

257
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:49,580
Move it!

258
00:13:52,630 --> 00:13:52,960
Move!

259
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:00,720
Hurry!

260
00:14:00,870 --> 00:14:01,240
Move!

261
00:14:07,870 --> 00:14:08,320
Move!

262
00:14:22,570 --> 00:14:23,320
Second Young Master Du,

263
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:24,850
what is the meaning of this?

264
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:26,630
You had someone

265
00:14:26,630 --> 00:14:28,490
deliver this jade pot to my daddy?

266
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:32,200
I don't know what you're talking about.

267
00:14:34,630 --> 00:14:35,480
Trying to lure

268
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:36,360
Du Chengrong out like this

269
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,200
won't work.

270
00:14:37,870 --> 00:14:39,000
Without an insider,

271
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:40,630
do you think he'd be foolish enough

272
00:14:40,630 --> 00:14:42,560
to come out alone to trade with you,

273
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:43,910
Xu Zhongyi?

274
00:14:49,720 --> 00:14:50,790
Second Young Master Du,

275
00:14:50,790 --> 00:14:52,390
I'm not quite following you.

276
00:14:57,390 --> 00:14:59,190
Since I even know your real name,

277
00:14:59,630 --> 00:15:01,630
naturally, I've also investigated

278
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:03,120
what happened back then.

279
00:15:05,510 --> 00:15:06,770
Who would have thought

280
00:15:07,120 --> 00:15:08,080
that our family's

281
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:08,880
first fortune

282
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:10,320
was all thanks to antiques

283
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:11,650
taken from your family?

284
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:14,840
My daddy always claimed

285
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:16,240
he started from scratch.

286
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:21,330
Turns out he relied on robbery.

287
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:25,630
After all these years,

288
00:15:25,630 --> 00:15:28,160
you still haven't succeeded in
your revenge.

289
00:15:28,380 --> 00:15:29,880
You should know how cunning

290
00:15:29,880 --> 00:15:30,950
that old fox is.

291
00:15:32,470 --> 00:15:34,440
You've endured for decades.

292
00:15:34,870 --> 00:15:36,440
Being impatient now

293
00:15:36,870 --> 00:15:39,270
will only expose
your true identity to him.

294
00:15:40,150 --> 00:15:41,960
What exactly do you want me to do?

295
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:49,790
I need you... to do me a favor.

296
00:15:59,270 --> 00:15:59,840
Mr. Qiu,

297
00:16:00,030 --> 00:16:02,030
you still came out on a day like this?

298
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:02,870
You don't have to

299
00:16:02,870 --> 00:16:04,720
push yourself this hard for business, eh?

300
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:05,360
Come on...

301
00:16:14,630 --> 00:16:15,200
Daddy.

302
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:16,750
Zhaoji.

303
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,880
When did you make this decision?

304
00:16:21,390 --> 00:16:22,320
These people...

305
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:25,640
Liu Keying gave them to you, didn't she?

306
00:16:28,170 --> 00:16:30,010
When did you two join forces?

307
00:16:33,270 --> 00:16:34,530
Why should we tell you?

308
00:16:39,910 --> 00:16:41,870
It started from the moment I realized

309
00:16:41,870 --> 00:16:43,360
you were going senile.

310
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:47,320
You're already old,

311
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:49,960
but you just refuse to give up power.

312
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,320
You just wanted to buy more time

313
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:52,510
for Zhaohui to grow,

314
00:16:52,510 --> 00:16:53,170
didn't you?

315
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:55,910
Don't you know what kind of person he is?

316
00:16:55,910 --> 00:16:57,430
You actually want to put

317
00:16:57,450 --> 00:16:58,780
such an idiot in charge?

318
00:17:00,390 --> 00:17:02,120
I need to correct your mistake.

319
00:17:02,630 --> 00:17:03,150
Mr. Du,

320
00:17:04,550 --> 00:17:06,069
you promised to marry me.

321
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:08,960
Why did you break your promise

322
00:17:08,960 --> 00:17:11,270
and make me the laughingstock
of the whole island?

323
00:17:11,270 --> 00:17:12,730
My brother, Liu Tianquan,

324
00:17:12,920 --> 00:17:14,920
worked like a slave for your family.

325
00:17:15,790 --> 00:17:16,920
Now that you're old

326
00:17:17,510 --> 00:17:19,829
and want to clear obstacles
for your first son,

327
00:17:19,829 --> 00:17:21,880
you just kick us siblings aside.

328
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:24,349
I begged you

329
00:17:24,349 --> 00:17:25,880
to spare my brother's life.

330
00:17:27,420 --> 00:17:28,880
What did you promise me?

331
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:40,030
Liu Keying.

332
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:43,960
How can you be this stupid?

333
00:17:44,200 --> 00:17:45,970
You've been by my side for over 10 years,

334
00:17:45,970 --> 00:17:47,840
yet you haven't learned from me

335
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:50,000
that you can't just trust

336
00:17:50,110 --> 00:17:51,640
anyone around you!

337
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:53,580
Think about it.

338
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:56,480
He's not even 23 yet,

339
00:17:57,110 --> 00:17:59,790
and he dares to treat his dad like this—

340
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:01,270
his own dad.

341
00:18:01,750 --> 00:18:03,160
Even if you have something on him,

342
00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:03,880
so what?

343
00:18:04,510 --> 00:18:06,840
You think that'll keep him under control?

344
00:18:10,200 --> 00:18:12,060
Looks like my choice was correct.

345
00:18:13,110 --> 00:18:15,510
Although Zhaohui can be reckless at times,

346
00:18:15,830 --> 00:18:19,790
he knows what he should

347
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:21,920
and shouldn't do.

348
00:18:22,750 --> 00:18:23,510
But you—

349
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:26,030
you're too greedy.

350
00:18:38,350 --> 00:18:40,830
A man who built his fortune
through robbery

351
00:18:41,830 --> 00:18:43,030
is calling me greedy?

352
00:18:45,270 --> 00:18:45,920
Daddy...

353
00:18:46,270 --> 00:18:47,680
Stop wasting words on him!

354
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:48,310
Do it!

355
00:18:56,070 --> 00:18:57,130
At a time like this,

356
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:59,570
don't you know who to point the guns at?

357
00:19:14,830 --> 00:19:16,160
You two scumbags,

358
00:19:16,160 --> 00:19:18,020
how dare you point your guns at me?

359
00:19:19,750 --> 00:19:21,030
What's wrong

360
00:19:21,030 --> 00:19:22,490
with pointing guns at you?

361
00:19:26,780 --> 00:19:27,510
Mr. Qiu.

362
00:19:29,550 --> 00:19:30,750
My surname isn't Qiu.

363
00:19:31,590 --> 00:19:34,310
My real name is Xu Zhongyi.

364
00:19:37,480 --> 00:19:38,790
Zhongyi, it's me.

365
00:19:39,390 --> 00:19:40,390
The boat is ready.

366
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:41,530
You can leave today.

367
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:47,790
Chengrong, the rain is so heavy outside.

368
00:19:47,790 --> 00:19:48,720
Is the boat safe?

369
00:19:53,310 --> 00:19:54,110
Du Chengrong,

370
00:19:54,320 --> 00:19:55,030
I've waited for this day

371
00:19:55,030 --> 00:19:56,110
for 30 years.

372
00:19:56,530 --> 00:19:57,180
Back then,

373
00:19:57,720 --> 00:19:58,920
you stole my antiques

374
00:19:59,240 --> 00:20:00,840
and killed my wife and child.

375
00:20:01,350 --> 00:20:04,110
You never expected
I'd live to see this day, did you?

376
00:20:04,110 --> 00:20:05,920
Today, I'm here to settle the score

377
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:07,720
and take back what belongs to me.

378
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:09,720
Du Chengrong,

379
00:20:10,200 --> 00:20:11,680
today is the day you die.

380
00:20:14,260 --> 00:20:15,510
Wait, let me gather my thoughts.

381
00:20:15,510 --> 00:20:16,230
I can't quite remember.

382
00:20:16,230 --> 00:20:17,110
You are...

383
00:20:20,160 --> 00:20:21,020
I remember now.

384
00:20:22,030 --> 00:20:23,240
Yes, I remember you!

385
00:20:24,310 --> 00:20:26,310
But today should not be the day I die.

386
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:45,080
You've been managing

387
00:20:45,270 --> 00:20:47,270
the company for the past two months.

388
00:20:47,640 --> 00:20:48,790
Since you have the ability

389
00:20:48,790 --> 00:20:50,200
to keep it from going bankrupt

390
00:20:50,200 --> 00:20:51,680
even during a stock market crash,

391
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:52,960
keep managing it.

392
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:57,370
You can announce to the public that...

393
00:20:58,590 --> 00:21:00,320
I've regained consciousness.

394
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:02,000
Also,

395
00:21:02,960 --> 00:21:04,200
let Vivi stay.

396
00:21:04,870 --> 00:21:05,680
You can go now.

397
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,880
You don't need to keep working so hard

398
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:09,350
pretending to be the dutiful son here.

399
00:21:09,350 --> 00:21:10,890
You're still thinking about Vivi?

400
00:21:10,890 --> 00:21:11,640
Let me tell you...

401
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:12,830
Don't think

402
00:21:12,850 --> 00:21:14,160
I'm unaware
of what's been going on in the family.

403
00:21:14,160 --> 00:21:15,440
Nothing gets past me!

404
00:21:22,170 --> 00:21:22,930
Anyway,

405
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:25,560
those people
who tried to kill you at the dock

406
00:21:25,560 --> 00:21:26,840
weren't sent by me.

407
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:31,370
They wanted to keep smuggling.

408
00:21:31,480 --> 00:21:32,690
I couldn't stop them.

409
00:21:33,280 --> 00:21:34,680
But I won't do it anymore.

410
00:21:49,120 --> 00:21:49,820
That's all.

411
00:21:50,490 --> 00:21:51,170
Xia Ziyu

412
00:21:51,200 --> 00:21:52,720
probably won't have it easy.

413
00:21:52,720 --> 00:21:54,390
If you insist on
bringing her back to Shengcheng,

414
00:21:54,390 --> 00:21:55,350
I don't think the old man

415
00:21:55,350 --> 00:21:56,400
will stop you.

416
00:21:56,750 --> 00:21:58,000
He might even help you.

417
00:21:58,000 --> 00:21:59,600
Then I'll thank him for that.

418
00:22:00,480 --> 00:22:02,740
But the matter between Xia Ziyu and me...

419
00:22:02,960 --> 00:22:04,290
I must settle it myself.

420
00:22:09,750 --> 00:22:10,510
Xu Zhongyi

421
00:22:10,880 --> 00:22:12,350
might not be able to
come back for a while.

422
00:22:12,350 --> 00:22:13,110
That's still better than

423
00:22:13,110 --> 00:22:14,170
never coming back.

424
00:22:22,680 --> 00:22:23,330
Thank you.

425
00:22:33,110 --> 00:22:33,510
Here.

426
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:35,750
Be careful.

427
00:22:35,800 --> 00:22:38,640
♪ Drifting with the wind and waves ♪

428
00:22:39,600 --> 00:22:42,440
♪ Drifting with the waves of life ♪

429
00:22:43,800 --> 00:22:46,990
♪ The moment our paths crossed ♪

430
00:22:47,740 --> 00:22:50,860
♪ We were instantly worlds apart ♪

431
00:22:51,800 --> 00:22:54,680
♪ Fate drifts with the wind ♪

432
00:22:52,480 --> 00:22:53,070
Xiaolan.

433
00:22:53,750 --> 00:22:54,680
Why are you here?

434
00:22:55,740 --> 00:22:58,700
♪ Watching over you even if fate ends ♪

435
00:22:55,790 --> 00:22:56,550
Wait here a moment.

436
00:22:56,550 --> 00:22:57,070
I'll go get the car.

437
00:22:57,070 --> 00:22:57,440
Okay.

438
00:22:57,720 --> 00:22:58,830
He'll bring the car here,

439
00:22:58,830 --> 00:22:59,680
then we'll go out.

440
00:22:59,650 --> 00:23:03,250
♪ The moment we gazed at each other ♪

441
00:22:59,680 --> 00:23:00,720
I'll be right back.

442
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:01,510
It's windy outside.

443
00:23:01,510 --> 00:23:02,970
Let's wait inside for now.

444
00:23:03,590 --> 00:23:07,120
♪ Tears fell in my heart ♪

445
00:23:03,680 --> 00:23:05,440
Let me fix your scarf.

446
00:23:06,160 --> 00:23:06,760
It's fine.

447
00:23:07,110 --> 00:23:07,640
Let's go.

448
00:23:07,710 --> 00:23:08,420
-Let's go.
-Okay.

449
00:23:07,930 --> 00:23:11,390
♪ Even as we part,
I give you all my heart ♪

450
00:23:11,450 --> 00:23:15,040
♪ Silently enduring the twists of fate ♪

451
00:23:15,840 --> 00:23:19,810
♪ Someday, perhaps,
we'll be together again ♪

452
00:23:19,840 --> 00:23:22,590
♪ Reliving the past ♪

453
00:23:23,850 --> 00:23:31,260
♪ And yet, we may never meet again ♪

454
00:23:31,860 --> 00:23:38,130
♪ The twilight sky in that distant land
feels even farther away ♪

455
00:23:39,740 --> 00:23:42,800
♪ Who stands on the golden shore? ♪

456
00:23:43,890 --> 00:23:47,050
♪ Who waits beyond the smoke of war? ♪

457
00:23:47,930 --> 00:23:51,300
♪ In that fleeting glance back ♪

458
00:23:51,910 --> 00:23:55,190
♪ We softly ask how we've fared ♪

459
00:24:10,550 --> 00:24:12,280
Did he ask you to give this to me?

460
00:24:16,110 --> 00:24:17,230
Uncle Xu said to

461
00:24:18,310 --> 00:24:19,840
give him a little more time,

462
00:24:20,750 --> 00:24:22,480
and he will come back to see you.

463
00:24:23,630 --> 00:24:25,490
Let this keep you company for now.

464
00:24:28,590 --> 00:24:29,270
Okay.

465
00:24:31,110 --> 00:24:33,110
As long as he's willing to come back.

466
00:24:34,400 --> 00:24:35,830
I've waited for so long.

467
00:24:37,650 --> 00:24:39,510
I don't mind waiting a bit longer.

468
00:24:46,920 --> 00:24:47,920
And there's this.

469
00:25:10,440 --> 00:25:10,920
"Mom,

470
00:25:12,030 --> 00:25:13,690
rest a while if you're tired."

471
00:25:21,310 --> 00:25:21,750
"Mom,

472
00:25:22,910 --> 00:25:24,020
I miss you so much."

473
00:25:32,960 --> 00:25:33,440
"Mom,

474
00:25:34,110 --> 00:25:36,170
you must take good care of yourself."

475
00:25:47,200 --> 00:25:47,680
"Mom,

476
00:25:48,590 --> 00:25:49,990
wait for me to come home."

477
00:26:08,270 --> 00:26:08,680
He...

478
00:26:11,400 --> 00:26:11,750
He...

479
00:26:14,240 --> 00:26:14,590
He...

480
00:26:14,640 --> 00:26:15,040
Why...

481
00:26:15,350 --> 00:26:17,980
Why has he become like this?

482
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:41,500
Mom will wait for you to come home.

483
00:26:44,790 --> 00:26:46,650
Mom will wait for you to come home.

484
00:27:20,670 --> 00:27:22,270
If I could go back in time,

485
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:25,680
if I could turn back time,

486
00:27:27,680 --> 00:27:28,440
would everything

487
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,640
have been different?

488
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:45,550
What's wrong?

489
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:50,250
Something on your mind?

490
00:27:53,000 --> 00:27:53,800
It's nothing.

491
00:27:55,160 --> 00:27:56,890
I just thought of an old friend.

492
00:28:05,110 --> 00:28:06,110
The hardest thing

493
00:28:07,480 --> 00:28:09,680
for anyone is facing themselves.

494
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:13,640
Once you overcome that,

495
00:28:16,270 --> 00:28:17,200
nothing else in this world

496
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:18,350
can stop you.

497
00:28:33,920 --> 00:28:34,510
Mr. Du!

498
00:28:35,300 --> 00:28:35,830
Mr. Du!

499
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:37,720
When can we interview you?

500
00:28:44,110 --> 00:28:45,440
Good day, Master!

501
00:28:48,790 --> 00:28:49,510
Leave us.

502
00:28:50,310 --> 00:28:51,040
Yes, Master!

503
00:29:04,400 --> 00:29:05,960
Master, I can explain.

504
00:29:06,350 --> 00:29:07,680
It's not what you think.

505
00:29:08,240 --> 00:29:08,640
I...

506
00:29:09,620 --> 00:29:10,920
Did Zhaohui

507
00:29:11,510 --> 00:29:12,310
send you outside

508
00:29:12,310 --> 00:29:13,710
to learn to act like this?

509
00:29:15,190 --> 00:29:16,080
Yes, yes.

510
00:29:16,200 --> 00:29:17,730
It was he who had me learn it.

511
00:29:18,350 --> 00:29:19,790
He also asked me to seduce Zhaoji

512
00:29:19,790 --> 00:29:20,920
to drive a wedge between you and...

513
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:21,440
Enough!

514
00:29:22,550 --> 00:29:23,960
How do you think I, Du Chengrong,

515
00:29:23,960 --> 00:29:25,400
got to where I am today?

516
00:29:26,200 --> 00:29:27,350
Do you think I care about

517
00:29:27,350 --> 00:29:28,720
those petty schemes?

518
00:29:29,750 --> 00:29:30,640
To me,

519
00:29:30,750 --> 00:29:31,310
you're just a pawn

520
00:29:31,310 --> 00:29:32,960
I abandoned long ago.

521
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:34,440
Xia Ziyu,

522
00:29:34,680 --> 00:29:35,510
the affairs of my family

523
00:29:35,510 --> 00:29:37,040
have nothing to do with you!

524
00:29:38,310 --> 00:29:39,240
No, Master.

525
00:29:40,160 --> 00:29:41,030
I'm Vivi.

526
00:29:41,550 --> 00:29:42,440
I'm Vivi.

527
00:29:43,160 --> 00:29:43,720
Vivi.

528
00:29:45,310 --> 00:29:46,200
Are you the Vivi

529
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:47,640
that I cherish,

530
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:50,830
or the fugitive Xia Ziyu?

531
00:29:50,830 --> 00:29:52,400
That all depends on my mood.

532
00:29:53,240 --> 00:29:54,300
Do you understand?

533
00:29:56,270 --> 00:29:57,020
Master, I was wrong.

534
00:29:57,020 --> 00:29:57,750
Master, I was wrong.

535
00:29:57,750 --> 00:29:58,920
I'll tell you the truth.

536
00:29:58,920 --> 00:30:00,880
It was Zhaoji who made me pull the plug.

537
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:01,880
He forced me to do it.

538
00:30:01,880 --> 00:30:02,480
If I hadn't done it,

539
00:30:02,480 --> 00:30:03,510
he would've killed me first!

540
00:30:03,510 --> 00:30:04,070
I was scared!

541
00:30:04,070 --> 00:30:05,880
He forced me, Master!

542
00:30:06,070 --> 00:30:07,550
So you're saying you're afraid of Zhaoji,

543
00:30:07,550 --> 00:30:08,680
but not afraid of me?

544
00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:10,640
I am.

545
00:30:10,940 --> 00:30:11,720
I am afraid.

546
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:12,240
I...

547
00:30:12,260 --> 00:30:13,900
I stayed by your side at the hospital
for two days.

548
00:30:13,900 --> 00:30:14,880
I thought you really

549
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:15,960
wouldn't wake up.

550
00:30:16,110 --> 00:30:18,240
That's why I listened to his nonsense.

551
00:30:19,350 --> 00:30:21,920
Zhaohui sent you to me,

552
00:30:22,350 --> 00:30:23,880
so I accepted that gesture

553
00:30:24,350 --> 00:30:26,350
and kept you around for amusement.

554
00:30:26,790 --> 00:30:28,250
Whatever you were before,

555
00:30:28,720 --> 00:30:30,120
or whatever you've done—

556
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:31,640
none of that matters to me.

557
00:30:32,510 --> 00:30:33,060
Master...

558
00:30:33,060 --> 00:30:34,660
I gave you wealth and status,

559
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:37,440
and you got to show off in public.

560
00:30:38,590 --> 00:30:39,790
Did you really think

561
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:41,680
that I trusted your abilities,

562
00:30:41,680 --> 00:30:42,720
or that

563
00:30:42,720 --> 00:30:44,720
I only favored you?

564
00:30:45,090 --> 00:30:45,550
Master,

565
00:30:45,550 --> 00:30:47,160
I don't want anything anymore.

566
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:48,440
I don't want anything anymore, Master!

567
00:30:48,440 --> 00:30:50,200
I just want to stay by your side,

568
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:50,660
Master!

569
00:30:50,880 --> 00:30:52,450
Please spare me this once!

570
00:30:52,480 --> 00:30:53,830
Spare me this once!

571
00:30:53,850 --> 00:30:55,480
Forgive you? Spare you?

572
00:30:55,590 --> 00:30:57,250
How am I supposed to spare you?

573
00:30:57,440 --> 00:30:59,370
Which one do you want me to forgive?

574
00:31:00,070 --> 00:31:02,070
The time
you and Zhaohui conspired to trick me,

575
00:31:02,070 --> 00:31:04,350
or the time you and Zhaoji conspired

576
00:31:04,350 --> 00:31:05,880
to kill me?

577
00:31:08,830 --> 00:31:10,350
I don't think you should stay here.

578
00:31:10,350 --> 00:31:11,400
You should go back

579
00:31:11,400 --> 00:31:12,530
to where you belong.

580
00:31:13,190 --> 00:31:13,760
No...

581
00:31:14,240 --> 00:31:14,680
No.

582
00:31:14,790 --> 00:31:15,790
I don't want to go back!

583
00:31:15,790 --> 00:31:16,750
I don't want to go back, Master!

584
00:31:16,750 --> 00:31:17,510
I'll be good!

585
00:31:17,510 --> 00:31:18,640
Master, I was wrong!

586
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:24,110
What?

587
00:31:24,830 --> 00:31:25,350
Scared?

588
00:31:26,510 --> 00:31:28,150
Scared that I'll send you away, right?

589
00:31:28,150 --> 00:31:28,880
No, no.

590
00:31:28,960 --> 00:31:29,720
No, I don't want to.

591
00:31:29,720 --> 00:31:31,000
No, I'm not going back!

592
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:32,430
I don't want to go back, Master!

593
00:31:32,430 --> 00:31:34,240
I don't want to go back, Master!

594
00:31:34,960 --> 00:31:36,760
You've always relied on others.

595
00:31:37,110 --> 00:31:38,400
This time, whether you live or die

596
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:39,380
depends on you.

597
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:41,920
Du Zhaoji

598
00:31:42,070 --> 00:31:43,480
has a forged will.

599
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:45,110
Go get it for me.

600
00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:49,750
You should know

601
00:31:50,390 --> 00:31:51,390
where he keeps it.

602
00:31:53,790 --> 00:31:54,790
Don't let me down.

603
00:32:23,880 --> 00:32:25,080
Everything's ready?

604
00:32:27,720 --> 00:32:29,400
Du Chengrong has insisted on
sending someone

605
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:30,400
to follow Xia Ziyu

606
00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:32,510
to ensure she doesn't run away midway.

607
00:32:32,510 --> 00:32:33,550
That actually

608
00:32:33,680 --> 00:32:34,820
works in our favor.

609
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:37,980
Du Chengrong is probably thinking that

610
00:32:37,980 --> 00:32:39,280
if your plan fails,

611
00:32:39,640 --> 00:32:40,680
he'll deal with Xia Ziyu

612
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:41,550
in his own way.

613
00:32:42,110 --> 00:32:43,240
He won't let this go.

614
00:32:43,680 --> 00:32:45,240
He won't make life easy for Xia Ziyu.

615
00:32:45,240 --> 00:32:47,030
Tell me, for Xia Ziyu,

616
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:49,270
which is worse:

617
00:32:49,510 --> 00:32:50,880
being dealt with by Du Chengrong

618
00:32:50,880 --> 00:32:52,280
or being dealt with by me?

619
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:54,920
If she falls into Du Chengrong's hands,

620
00:32:55,110 --> 00:32:57,510
she might be thrown back
to the Walled City.

621
00:32:57,720 --> 00:32:59,320
If she falls into your hands,

622
00:32:59,790 --> 00:33:01,390
she has to face her past self.

623
00:33:01,640 --> 00:33:02,830
I just want her to face

624
00:33:02,830 --> 00:33:05,160
everything she's been running away from.

625
00:33:09,960 --> 00:33:10,790
Going out?

626
00:33:12,480 --> 00:33:13,440
Come back early.

627
00:33:14,030 --> 00:33:16,860
I managed to buy a free-range chicken
from the countryside.

628
00:33:16,860 --> 00:33:17,270
Okay.

629
00:33:17,720 --> 00:33:19,320
We'll try to come back early.

630
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:19,960
Okay.

631
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:21,660
Call your mom over too.

632
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:23,560
The soup she makes is better.

633
00:33:24,030 --> 00:33:24,440
Okay.

634
00:33:24,890 --> 00:33:25,550
We're heading out now.

635
00:33:25,550 --> 00:33:25,960
Okay.

636
00:33:26,240 --> 00:33:27,010
Bye, Granny Yu.

637
00:33:27,010 --> 00:33:27,870
Bye, Granny Yu.

638
00:33:52,070 --> 00:33:53,480
You will never beat me.

639
00:34:24,949 --> 00:34:26,199
Ms. Vivi, please.

640
00:34:40,960 --> 00:34:41,880
Hello, Mom.

641
00:34:42,510 --> 00:34:43,880
Ge Jian will pick you up in a while

642
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:45,150
