643
00:34:45,150 --> 00:34:46,710
Zhenzhu will go there too.

644
00:34:46,920 --> 00:34:48,760
She wants to talk to you about Luna.

645
00:34:48,760 --> 00:34:49,190
Okay.

646
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:51,710
Tonight I want to have the soup you make.

647
00:34:51,710 --> 00:34:53,040
Wait for me there, okay?

648
00:34:53,550 --> 00:34:54,000
Okay.

649
00:34:55,840 --> 00:34:56,280
Bye.

650
00:34:59,550 --> 00:35:00,550
Was that Xiaolan?

651
00:35:01,630 --> 00:35:03,360
She said she wants chicken soup

652
00:35:03,590 --> 00:35:06,230
and asked me to go to Granny Yu's
to make it for her.

653
00:35:06,230 --> 00:35:07,280
Since she arranged it,

654
00:35:07,280 --> 00:35:08,540
