657
00:35:12,960 --> 00:35:13,490
Alright.

658
00:35:15,360 --> 00:35:16,090
Is that okay?

659
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:17,340
More than okay.

660
00:35:20,760 --> 00:35:21,280
Go.

661
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:23,090
The goodbye ritual.

662
00:35:25,160 --> 00:35:27,680
Don't talk to strangers outside.

663
00:35:27,710 --> 00:35:29,510
Don't accept candy from anyone.

664
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:30,590
This ritual?

665
00:35:33,760 --> 00:35:34,720
Alright, alright, alright.

666
00:35:34,720 --> 00:35:35,280
See you tonight.

667
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:36,210
See you tonight.

668
00:35:40,360 --> 00:35:41,960
Du Zhaoji has been arrested.

669
00:35:42,190 --> 00:35:44,280
Xia Ziyu is coming to Shengcheng alone.

670
00:35:44,280 --> 00:35:46,680
Aren't you worried she might have helpers?

671
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:47,590
I don't know.

672
00:35:48,630 --> 00:35:49,490
On Kong Island,

673
00:35:50,070 --> 00:35:53,000
