trying to get close to Du Chengrong.

674
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:54,480
The fact that Xia Ziyu pulled it off

675
00:35:54,480 --> 00:35:56,070
means she's got both cunning

676
00:35:56,070 --> 00:35:56,840
and brains.

677
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:58,800
With Du Zhaoji arrested,

678
00:35:58,880 --> 00:35:59,590
