684
00:36:21,440 --> 00:36:22,200
No! Go away!

685
00:36:21,530 --> 00:36:23,680
[Shengcheng]

686
00:36:22,230 --> 00:36:22,830
Thank you.

687
00:36:22,830 --> 00:36:23,490
No! Go away!

688
00:36:24,060 --> 00:36:24,880
Thank you.

689
00:36:33,550 --> 00:36:34,190
Thank you.

690
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:36,880
Spare some change for food, please?

691
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:39,840
Please spare some change for food.

692
00:36:39,840 --> 00:36:40,630
Please spare some change for food.

693
00:36:40,630 --> 00:36:41,560
I lost this hand.

694
00:36:41,630 --> 00:36:42,210
I lost this hand.

695
00:36:42,210 --> 00:36:44,270
Please s-spare some change for food.

696
00:36:45,900 --> 00:36:47,310
