Please have pity on me.]

697
00:36:47,210 --> 00:36:48,940
Ziyu, you got into university?

698
00:36:49,550 --> 00:36:51,410
My daughter got into university.

699
00:36:52,150 --> 00:36:53,350
You're our village's

700
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:55,010
