701
00:37:10,440 --> 00:37:12,370
Please spare some change for food.

702
00:37:16,440 --> 00:37:17,040
Thank you.

703
00:37:17,480 --> 00:37:18,070
Thank you.

704
00:37:18,070 --> 00:37:18,530
Go away!

705
00:37:18,760 --> 00:37:19,710
Go away!

706
