713
00:37:51,710 --> 00:37:54,320
It's right there.
I want you to buy one for me.

714
00:37:54,440 --> 00:37:55,400
Alright. Wait here.

715
00:37:55,400 --> 00:37:56,660
I'll go buy one for you.

716
00:37:58,410 --> 00:37:59,670
Roasted sweet potatoes!

717
00:37:59,670 --> 00:38:02,320
Delicious, hot roasted sweet potatoes!

718
00:38:03,000 --> 00:38:04,360
Roasted sweet potatoes!

719
00:38:04,360 --> 00:38:06,920
Delicious, hot roasted sweet potatoes!

720
00:38:09,900 --> 00:38:10,530
Ziyu...

721
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:14,930
This is real, right?

722
00:38:15,840 --> 00:38:17,480
I'm so happy for you.

723
00:38:18,480 --> 00:38:19,590
I'm so proud of you.

724
00:38:22,250 --> 00:38:23,730
Roasted sweet potatoes!

725
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:26,360
Delicious, hot roasted sweet potatoes!

726
00:38:27,280 --> 00:38:28,680
Roasted sweet potatoes!

727
00:38:28,960 --> 00:38:30,490
Get a roasted sweet potato!

728
00:38:48,100 --> 00:38:49,480
Roasted sweet potatoes!

729
00:38:49,480 --> 00:38:51,530
Roasted sweet potatoes! Wanna try a piece?

730
00:38:51,530 --> 00:38:52,920
Roasted sweet potatoes!

731
00:38:52,920 --> 00:38:54,960
Freshly roasted sweet potatoes!

732
