751
00:40:10,760 --> 00:40:11,630
I'll wait outside.

752
00:40:11,630 --> 00:40:13,070
Call me if you need anything.

753
00:40:13,070 --> 00:40:13,670
Thank you.

754
00:40:43,240 --> 00:40:45,230
[To: Xia Xiaolan]

755
00:41:12,070 --> 00:41:12,600
Jianhua,

756
00:41:13,190 --> 00:41:14,230
this is our Dahe Village's

757
00:41:14,230 --> 00:41:15,430
rice field this year.

758
00:41:15,710 --> 00:41:16,760
Growing quite well.

759
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:17,800
Looks like the harvest this year

760
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:18,660
