775
00:41:39,630 --> 00:41:40,630
Hello, everyone!

776
00:41:40,800 --> 00:41:43,400
Working hard under this hot sun—
that's tough!

777
00:41:43,510 --> 00:41:44,230
Not at all.

778
00:41:44,400 --> 00:41:45,000
Not at all.

779
00:41:45,110 --> 00:41:45,640
Jianhua,

780
00:41:45,840 --> 00:41:46,880
let's go check over there.

781
00:41:46,880 --> 00:41:47,230
Okay.

782
00:41:47,880 --> 00:41:49,590
The timing of each season is also crucial.

783
00:41:49,590 --> 00:41:50,110
Well...

784
00:41:50,670 --> 00:41:52,230
When will he go back to the city?

785
00:41:52,230 --> 00:41:53,000
Who knows?

786
00:41:53,480 --> 00:41:54,840
Maybe after staying here for a long time,

787
00:41:54,840 --> 00:41:55,470
