if he married a wife here and stayed.

789
00:41:56,880 --> 00:41:57,480
Marry who?

790
00:41:57,550 --> 00:41:58,190
You?

791
00:41:58,840 --> 00:41:59,510
He's from the city.

792
00:41:59,510 --> 00:42:00,770
He has high standards.

793
00:42:00,880 --> 00:42:02,320
