801
00:42:31,510 --> 00:42:34,190
This is a love letter for Xiaolan?

802
00:42:34,940 --> 00:42:35,960
No, it's not.

803
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:38,410
Ziyu,

804
00:42:38,440 --> 00:42:40,570
did you just say you needed something?

805
00:42:43,670 --> 00:42:44,320
Jianhua,

806
00:42:45,280 --> 00:42:47,140
actually, I've always liked you.

807
00:43:09,150 --> 00:43:10,630
I mean every word.

808
00:43:10,920 --> 00:43:12,580
I've liked you for a long time.

809
00:43:50,670 --> 00:43:51,330
Movie time!

810
00:43:51,380 --> 00:43:52,310
It's movie time.

811
00:43:59,660 --> 00:44:00,870
Xia Ziyu

812
00:44:01,150 --> 00:44:03,280
has always been exceptionally proud.

813
00:44:03,840 --> 00:44:05,440
Relying on her little tricks,

814
00:44:05,440 --> 00:44:08,040
she'd monopolized
Grandma Xia's affections.

815
00:44:08,150 --> 00:44:09,670
She naturally assumed

816
00:44:09,960 --> 00:44:11,320
that all the best things

817
00:44:11,840 --> 00:44:12,880
should be hers.

818
00:44:13,920 --> 00:44:15,180
But she never expected

819
00:44:15,590 --> 00:44:17,320
that the one she had always dismissed—

820
00:44:17,320 --> 00:44:19,380
the seemingly carefree Xia Xiaolan—

821
00:44:20,360 --> 00:44:22,090
would win Wang Jianhua's heart

822
00:44:22,280 --> 00:44:23,590
before she could.

823
00:44:25,190 --> 00:44:25,960
Of course, Xia Ziyu

824
00:44:25,960 --> 00:44:27,290
liked Wang Jianhua too.

825
00:44:29,110 --> 00:44:30,550
But the moment she saw

826
00:44:30,550 --> 00:44:31,550
that love letter,

827
00:44:33,000 --> 00:44:34,150
what she wanted more

828
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:37,530
was the thrill
of stealing Wang Jianhua away.

829
00:45:01,710 --> 00:45:02,670
It really is you.
